name: DaLMatian
long_description:
DaLMatian is the first autonomous AI data analyst. We're building a multi-step reasoning agent that combines text-to-sql, segmentation, anomaly detection, and other tools to help decision makers generate more revenue.

Founded by three friends who met in undergrad at Princeton, our experience includes AI at Google Research, engineering at Google & Duolingo, quant trading at Virtu, and analytics at Riskified.
one_liner: The first autonomous AI data analyst agent
